<dl id="n03003c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03003c">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03003c"> 3(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Columbanus / squirrel in cowl</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> Legends tell us that he <font color="green">[Columbanus]</font> had a fascination for animals &hellip; and that the <mark>squirrels came down from the trees and nestled in his cowl</mark>. <small> J.M. Flood, <a name="JMFI" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#JMFI"><cite title="source">Ireland: Its Saints and Scholars</cite></a> (n.d) 35</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
